## Changelog

### Version 1.0.0 (2025)
- Major refactoring to class-based architecture
- Added specialized formatter classes (BasicFormatter, CaseFormatter, TransformationFormatter, GenerationFormatter, NormalizationFormatter)
- Added analyzer classes (CharacterAnalyzer, SentenceAnalyzer, ReadabilityAnalyzer, StatisticsAnalyzer, LanguageAnalyzer)
- Migrated from unittest to pytest
- Added comprehensive test coverage (102 tests)
- Improved documentation and examples
- Added case conversion methods (snake_case, camelCase, PascalCase, etc.)
- Added text transformation features (reversal, line operations, find/replace)
- Added text generation features (Lorem Ipsum, number spelling, currency formatting)
- Added text analysis features (readability metrics, statistics, language detection)
- Added text normalization features (Unicode, accents, smart quotes)

### Version 0.1.0 (Initial Release)
- Basic text formatting functions
- Function-based API
